version_description:
You can now share your Qudo profile directly to Snapchat.
We have also fixed a few small bugs and made the app faster!

- Discovery View: Find new friends even faster, using the new Discovery Grid View.
- New Profile View: You can now view someone's full profile before and after you've requested their Snap name.
- You can also mark other Users as favourite to find them more easily later on.

• Photo Verification: Users can now add a verification to their profile to show they're legit.
• A few small bug have also been fixed.
